                    <div className="mt-4">
                       <div className="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                          <FaCheck className="text-success me-2" />
                          <span><strong>Zero Collisions:</strong> For practical purposes, you can assume no two UUIDs will ever be the same.</span>
                       </div>
                       <div className="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
